* Harlow Gallery, home of the Kennebec Valley Art Association (founded in 1963)
* Hubbard Free Library
* Kennebec Ice Arena
* Kennebec Lodge No. 5 A.F. &amp; A.M., Masonic lodge chartered in Hallowell by Paul Revere in 1796
* Powder House Lot
* Row House
* St. Matthew&#x27;s Episcopal Church
