<doc id="116058" wikidata="Q9003431" url="?curid=116058" title="Hibberts Gore, Maine">
<text>Hibberts Gore (also called Hibberts) is a gore in Lincoln County, Maine, United States. The gore&#x27;s population was one as of the 2020 United States census.

==History==
Ignored by the surveyors who mapped Maine, it is one of many locales in Maine that remained unincorporated as most of the rest of the state was divided into cities, towns, and plantations.

==Demographics==

As of the 2020 census, there was 1 person, 1 household, and 0 families in Hibberts Gore.

==See also==
*Monowi, Nebraska – an incorporated village with a population of one.

